  <brief_title>AVAPS-AE Algorithm in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>AVAPS-AE COPD</acronym>
  <official_title>Engineering Validation of the AVAPS-AE Algorithm in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)Patients</official_title>
