  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Change in TCO2 measurement from baseline to 2 weeks post AVAPS-AE mode of therapy and change in TCO2 measurement from baseline to 6 weeks post AVAP-AE mode of therapy</measure>
    <time_frame>Baseline study, 2 week study and after 6 weeks of therapy</time_frame>
    <description>The baseline bilevel sleep study data and the AVAPS-AE sleep study data (from Baseline, 2 week and 6 week visits) will be analyzed to ascertain adequate control of nocturnal ventilation via mean overnight TcCO2 measurements.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Actigraphy</measure>
    <time_frame>2 weeks prior to the Baseline Sleep study</time_frame>
