  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age greater than or equal to 18 years

          -  Diagnosis of COPD

          -  Currently using a Bilevel device

          -  Documentation of medical stability by PI

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects, who are acutely ill, medically complicated or who are medically unstable

          -  Subjects in whom PAP therapy is otherwise medically contraindicated

          -  Subjects who have had surgery of the upper airway, nose, sinus, or middle ear within
             the previous 90 days

          -  Subjects with untreated, non-OSA sleep disorders, including but not limited to;
             insomnia, periodic limb movement syndrome, or restless leg syndrome (PLMI &gt; 10)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
